        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A short energy statement for the moment before accepting work that doesn't feel like the right fit. Two statements: one to release the scarcity pull, one to name what you're opening to.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to energy statements? Read ",
